    "description": "CDAC Consulting Pvt Ltd, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Senior Software Engineer for our Jaipur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout CDAC Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nCDAC Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Docker\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with CDAC Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
